{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":584145,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"您好，学弟在树洞被挂的时候，很多人的态度是哪怕99%实锤也不能挂真名，请不要张口就来","timestamp":1605835494,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584151,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"👍🏻","timestamp":1605835523,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584170,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"👍🏻","timestamp":1605835633,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584190,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"以及在第二天晚上之前，树洞的表现还是比较正常的，这个时候的诉求还只是要求学姐实名道歉，失控的开始是第二天晚上有人把这上升到了美院的问题","timestamp":1605835756,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584198,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"张口就来，树个假靶子打","timestamp":1605835825,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584214,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"该事件我从头到尾一直在关注，期间许多人在树洞上的言论的确是值得批判的，但我觉得dz的描述是不太符合事实的","timestamp":1605835922,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584269,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有正义感是好事，批判别人不能靠着不知第几手的消息就做审判，这是对的，但同样的，我觉得dz也不能靠着二手消息就觉得时间初期，树洞上的人就已经在煽风点火了。我支持把有些人批判一番，但不能这样。","timestamp":1605836358,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584315,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"您往前翻翻，统计一下，看看到底是不是如您说臆想的树洞如何煽风点火云云，整个二手小心，内心再邪恶揣测一番，没啥意思","timestamp":1605836790,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584657,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":121577,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 同意你的观点","timestamp":1605839143,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":121577,"reply":9,"tag":null,"text":"女生发朋友圈，说被骚扰，你们呼喊着要人肉，要小色狼受死。\n\n剧情翻转后，你们又呼喊着要人肉，要美院渣女受死。\n\n如果再翻转呢，没事，换个人受死罢了，反正藏在屏幕后面做审判很过瘾。\n\n看着网络上不知道第几手的信息，就都成了包青天狄仁杰替天行道了？\n\n都说学姐你为什么不等等监控证据确凿？吃瓜群众都等不及了呢","timestamp":1605835372,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}